"""
OUTLOOK DRAFT BOT (NO LLM) — VSCode-friendly (Python 3.14)
Purpose:
- Creates a draft reply for emails whose subject is exactly "bot" (case-insensitive).
- Uses ONLY KB documents (no email-chain docs) to extract relevant snippets.
- Inserts a "Verification Pack" at the bottom of the draft so you can run Microsoft 365 Copilot
  to verify + rewrite + translate (DE/EN) inside Outlook.

How you use it:
1) Run this script from VSCode (NOT a notebook).
2) Send an email to yourself with subject "bot" and a question in body.
3) Script creates a Draft reply + marks the original email as Read + categories it.
4) Open the draft in Outlook → use Copilot with the included prompt.

Dependencies:
- pywin32
- python-docx (only if you keep .docx in KB)
- pdfplumber or pypdf (optional for PDF KB)
- openpyxl (optional for Excel KB)
"""

